data.description: This 3BR, 2BA Ranch home has been wonderfully transformed over the last 6 years!  A new roof was installed in 2013, all Appliances (including Washer/Dryer and Water Heater) were replaced in 2016.  In 2017 the Kitchen got a new Quartz Counter and Tiled backsplash;  New tile work was installed behind the Living Room Wood Stove; All windows were replaced and both Bathrooms were remodeled.  In 2018 a new HVAC system was installed.  The entire home has recently been painted as well and all new ceiling Fans added!  The Family Room features a wood Fireplace, and a Wet Bar.  The 3 season Sun Room provides 384 extra square footage to the home and opens to an expansive deck and backyard!  The Garage is 28' x 29' and features one larger door to get a high profile vehicle inside!  Just minutes to schools, restaurants, and shopping!
